::Savanna::

She started to move slowly.  The pain was intense. She looked over 
and saw Spitfire in stasis lock a few feet away.  She slowly got up.  
She looked at the bounty hunters.  Despite the pain from the blast, 
she ran at Imprisoner.  She slashed at him with her claws.
